    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/af4e24bca884257a347da8956a6462f7.poster.avif?t=1738371308\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/af4e24bca884257a347da8956a6462f7.webm?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/af4e24bca884257a347da8956a6462f7.mp4?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>《机核吞噬者》</strong>是一款科幻轻度肉鸽游戏，你将捕猎成群的机械体，吸收它们的核心，成为星球上最强的机械生命。在本款游戏中，你可以解锁各具特色的武器与装备，创造出独属于自己的强化组合。随着一次次的选择越变越强，成为破格级别的存在。探索程序生成的环境场景，最终揭开这个末世的秘密。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/1d576cfa76e3163560fd94637284d1ef.poster.avif?t=1738371308\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/1d576cfa76e3163560fd94637284d1ef.webm?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/1d576cfa76e3163560fd94637284d1ef.mp4?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在数以百计的强化道具中做出选择，配合多种独特的武器，打造不同的战斗风格，组建独属于你的构筑。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/9f483731b7f5e5c661092313d9c99ef6.poster.avif?t=1738371308\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/9f483731b7f5e5c661092313d9c99ef6.webm?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/9f483731b7f5e5c661092313d9c99ef6.mp4?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>机械体们同样觊觎着你的核心，会从四面八方发动进攻，其中也不乏强大的精英敌人。要小心，它们具有特殊的行动模式！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/3e6cacd99a3f89e94b41e42fb7abf1f9.poster.avif?t=1738371308\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/3e6cacd99a3f89e94b41e42fb7abf1f9.webm?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199060/extras/3e6cacd99a3f89e94b41e42fb7abf1f9.mp4?t=1738371308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过探索地图、击败敌人并吸收核心来解锁成就并获取资源，从而制作更多的武器与装置。也不要忘记升级它们，以发挥出更加强大的力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>各具特色的武器</strong>：从众多具有独特能力的武器中做出选择。<br></li><li><strong>程序生成的地图</strong>：探索<strong>《机核吞噬者》</strong>多样的程序化世界。 <br></li><li><strong>永无止境的构筑</strong>：尝试各种强化道具间的组合，组建最佳的破格构筑。<br></li><li><strong>循序渐进的养成</strong>：逐步解锁武器与装置，强化自身能力。</li></ul>",
